{"tid":1293322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求Fact check","createTime":"2019-07-07T15:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T15:54:01.000Z","uid":272085,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5059a765c3a131755362fab1f06126743672a932","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"頭先立場直播影到警員PC16676指：<br />\n「如果有一隊警員執行職務時，警方只需要顯示其中一位警員既委任證就可以。」<br />\n<br />\n如果真係咁，咁冇證既就可以被包庇，不需被秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n請各位fact check."},{"pid":"47543c5542657d9bb089a6361ca9038e7c4b5d35","tid":1293322,"uid":65409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92264b03e2a15cfdad3c9dd10c5fb510a93bbf5e","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"199a76e69270ba30e8dcf445fdf991c608a2f905","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"da385e263af0fdac6a4195155ba9b54d271fc57d","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"89c9c88ce7487482a10ba8e241979d32eb3a2d4b","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"6b9f967ba7d30c0a284ef30a0d50c595b9e0224b","tid":1293322,"uid":139550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"fact check"},{"pid":"5f106913c1435cebeb402a49420773ecfe2200f5","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"103876892d473575279e53546cdea5b7cf45fd9f","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"4ed5f2b4fc4c4aaedd94d39cd5b499afccc90940","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"34f639cc52fd572b291f3ffcdcb656e7abd8a301","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"2defa18365128637c44ce65ebe9aa2504d68c6e6","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"933704a87256f3fb4baba5c0ff2dea71ea9a6c73","tid":1293322,"uid":272085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"91cf6bca9733ea033ea29c516a2719ab45b7051d","tid":1293322,"uid":18965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F13_faqs%2Ffaq_g.html&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=b6c86a88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html</a><br />\n<br />\n5.如何辨認警務人員之身份/警察委任證之真偽？<br />\n<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n<br />\n便衣警務人員：在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警務人員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n當警務人員出示委任證，只須向提出要求的市民展示委任證，而不可將委任證轉交任何市民查閱。 如市民對警務人員身份或委任證存有懷疑，可立即聯絡就近警署 查詢。<br />\n　　警察委任證特徵如下：<br />\n<br />\n正面印有(包括中英文) ：　　<br />\n香港警察、　　<br />\n彩色警徽、　　<br />\n警務人員姓名、職級、僱員號碼、　　<br />\n相片，另有香港警察及HONG KONG POLICE 字眼的鐳射標記。　<br />\n<br />\n　<br />\n背面印有以下聲明：「本證持有人是經正式委任的香港警察，其相片及資料載於背面。」<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n(有關警察委任證之警訊片段&ndash; (冒警騙案))<br />\n<br />\n我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d51a6334455e7b4000d03c672044687153c3c4","tid":1293322,"uid":3734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"咁即係下次係現場著同一套衫就可以做到狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367be79cbecb090c3e2fe4663bf03f2bd18a41f6","tid":1293322,"uid":268460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPO9sZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPO9sZa.png&h=0f0c2e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24550fd5788b0b73c2859bf877cd51161e6a4690","tid":1293322,"uid":85803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}